	@* Overview Section *@
	<section id="overview">
		<h2 class="doc-section">Overview</h2>
		<p>
			<code>PDTiles</code> is an isometric tile grid component for displaying connected tiles with logos.
			It renders a 3D-style grid using pure SVG with animated connectors, configurable appearance, and
			interactive click events. The component is ideal for:
		</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Product/service showcases with visual connections</li>
			<li>Dashboard backgrounds with animated elements</li>
			<li>Interactive diagrams showing relationships between items</li>
			<li>Hero sections with dynamic visual effects</li>
		</ul>

		<h4>Key Features</h4>
		<ul>
			<li><strong>Isometric 3D rendering</strong> - Pure SVG-based rendering with no external dependencies</li>
			<li><strong>Animated connectors</strong> - Bezier curves and straight lines with multiple fill patterns</li>
			<li><strong>Per-tile customization</strong> - Override colors, depth, visibility for individual tiles</li>
			<li><strong>Responsive scaling</strong> - Automatic or manual scaling with alignment options</li>
			<li><strong>Child content overlay</strong> - Place HTML content over the tile grid</li>
			<li><strong>Interactive</strong> - Click events for tiles and connectors</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

